These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, fanta, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, dancing, skydiving, video-games
1. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking lemonade##7
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice       | sprite | lemonade        |
| Hobby      | skydiving  | dancing | video-games        | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, ferret, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, baseball, water-polo, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the person who's sport is water-polo and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | ferret | turtle       | goldfish         | rat     |
| Sport   | baseball   | lacrosse | water-polo | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, epic, animation, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, r&b, country, jazz
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the fan of punk##7
3. the fan of country is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person watching epic movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | romance | animation | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre   | country | punk  | jazz   | r&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, photography, hiking, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, sailing, badminton, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | photography | puzzles | video-games       | hiking |
| Sport   | sailing      | rowing   | badminton | parkour  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, gardening, puzzles, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, french, indonesian, colombian
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
2. the russian is somewhere to the left of the french##5
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is writing##7
5. the colombian is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the french is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | writing   | sudoku | gardening |
| Nationality   | russian      | french | colombian      | indonesian |

