.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, fanta, water
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, pakistani, thai, turkish
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the thai##1
2. the thai is the person drinking water##1
3. the pakistani is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the turkish is somewhere between the brazilian and the pakistani##7
7. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade | hot-chocolate      | fanta | water     |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | turkish | pakistani   | thai |

