.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, mango, avocado, banana
There are 4 different nationalities: french, australian, japanese, malaysian
1. the french is on the far left##1
2. the person eating mango is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person eating banana is on the far left or far right##3
4. the malaysian is somewhere between the person eating peas and the person eating avocado##7
5. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the person eating avocado##5
6. the malaysian is on the left or right of the japanese##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | banana    | peas   | mango | avocado  |
| Nationality   | french | japanese | malaysian    | australian |

