2. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
3. the malaysian is the owner of the pony##1
4. the pakistani is somewhere between the malaysian and the british##7
5. the german is on the left of the british##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | pakistani | german | british |
| Pet           | pony   | turtle    | hedgehog       | goat  |

