2. the person watching spy movies is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
3. the owner of the goldfish is not the person watching documentary movies##6
4. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | adventure | spy | documentary |
