2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the fan of jazz##2
6. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person watching disaster movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | martial-arts | disaster | zombie   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | salsa      | punk      | hip-hop |

