3. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person who's hobby is cooking##6
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
