2. the person who's hobby is camping is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person driving the roller##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | camping | woodworking | singing | drawing |
| Transport   | van   | scooter      | roller        | motorbike  |

