The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, classical, blues, trance
1. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
2. the fan of trance is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the fan of blues##7
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
4. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up   | sprite | lemonade | iced-tea   |
| Music-Genre   | folk | blues   | trance | classical |

