3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
6. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
