.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, guinea-pig, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, jet-ski, roller
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the owner of the fish##7
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | fish    | guinea-pig | chinchilla     | lizard |
| Transport   | jet-ski | roller  | train | skateboard |

 